  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Bifurian</span> Silk is an extr=
emely
  fine shimmering blue silk, spun by the <span class=3DSpellE>Bifuria</span>
  worm.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Bifuria</span> worms live deep =
in dark
  underground caves on Continental worlds. They attach themselves to the ce=
iling
  and walls of damp grottos and spin vast webs of ultra-fine gossamer <span
  class=3DSpellE>fibers</span>. These <span class=3DSpellE>fibers</span> ca=
n be
  collected and woven into <span class=3DSpellE>Bifurian</span> silk.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Occurrence: very rare</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Type: Luxury Resource<span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso=
-ansi-language:
  EN-GB'><o:p></o:p></span></p>
